</HTML></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#112512><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub16.ezboard.com/uearthpig95.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Earthpig95</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_thatch.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Druzzil Ro Member</span><br>  Posts: 87<br> <font color=#CCCCC8>(11/20/01 5:55:55 pm)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://www.geocities.com/Sir_Vikin/dda4.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Quick question for Warrior types </span><hr size=1> I used 2hded weapons from 20 to 40 because I had bad 1hders. The Taunt skill still works and the Dmg bonus on your main hand isn't high enough to make fast weapons that good. I would say stick with your 2hders. A nice cheap Mith staff was my best friend from 29 to 40.<br>
